blp2bmp
-----------
This command line tool can convert textures enclosed in BLP files (Blizzard's 
texture format) into ordinary 32bpp BMP image. DXT1/3/5 compression methods 
are supported. Command syntax listed as below:

    Usage: blp2bmp [-i | -a] <blp_file>
           -i      dump blp2 header
	       -a      convert all mipmaps

